rows.label: qst710102_msg0001
rows.name: Hey! Did you catch any insects?

rows.label: qst710102_msg0101
rows.name:
Nice! That's more than enough!
Thanks so much!

rows.label: qst710102_msg0102
rows.name:
If I can boil these up and get her to
drink it, then maybe, just maybe...

rows.label: qst710102_msg0104
rows.name:
I'm also partial to tinkering with
machinery!

rows.label: qst710102_msg0105
rows.name:
Lemme thank you properly. I'll show
you a pretty amazing invention of mine!

rows.label: qst710102_msg0201
rows.name:
I need more insects, lots more!
Come back when you've found some!

rows.label: qst710102_msg0202
rows.name:
In particular, I'm looking for a flashy,
fluttery kind of insect. If you find one
like that, bring it to me, PLEASE!
